curlew
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:2
Definition:godwit, kuaka, southern godwit, <i>Limosa Novae Zealandiae </i> (not the rare straggler, the Australian Curlew' <i>Numenius cyanopus</i>, 1888 Buller 2/45).
